2.Simple Calculator 

 function [sum,sub,Mul,div]=operations(x,y)
 sum=x+y;
 sub=x-y;
 Mul=x*y;
 div=x/y;
 end
 
 output:
  
 [sum,sub,Mul,div]=functions(6,2)
